results.name: Coefficients in expansion of 1/E_4^(1/8).
link: Seiichi Manyama, Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..424
formula: a(0) = 1, a(n) = (1/n)*Sum_{k=1..n} A300147(k)*a(n-k) for n > 0. - _Seiichi Manyama_, Feb 27 2018
